flowchart LR
  User[🧍 User's Browser]
  subgraph FE[Front End]
    React[⚛️ React: UI Components]
    Vite[Vite: Dev Server & Bundler]
  end
  subgraph BE[Back End]
    FastAPI[⚙️ FastAPI: APIs & Business Logic]
    DB[(💾 Database)]
  end

  User -->|clicks/buttons| React
  React -->|fetch() JSON over HTTP| FastAPI
  FastAPI --> DB
  DB --> FastAPI
  FastAPI -->|JSON response| React
  React --> User
